**Date stamp:** Include "Last reviewed: [Month Year]" at the top of the article, below the H1, before the first H2.

**Internal linking:** Include at minimum one internal link to another brightplace knowledgebase article. If no directly relevant article exists, insert [INTERNAL LINK PLACEHOLDER] with a topic description so the editorial team can assign the correct URL before publication.

**No external links to:** ILS platforms, review aggregators, score sites, forums, or any direct competitor. Permissible external links: government housing resources, academic or nonprofit research, original data sources. When in doubt, omit rather than link.